âœ… Bonus (Force HTTPS via .htaccess if needed)
In /var/www/html/.htaccess:

RewriteEngine On
RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]


